Program: Last Word
Title: In a special edition of Last Word, Matthew Bannister talks to obituary editors from around the UK about the nature of their work
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b04vjh88
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Dec 2014
Matthew Bannister and a group of obituary editors from around the UK gather to compare notes and discuss why the world of the obituary writer is very often an uplifting one. Producer: Neil George.